{"tid":229230,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴: 中資能掌控香港經濟 多派移民過去 香港01 : 海底撈福利好","createTime":"2017-05-04T12:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T14:49:50.000Z","uid":49359,"like":41,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3e63000e18bbacb58165efe65b92c67e31462c9f","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:42:48.000Z","msg":"海底撈都講開好耐<br />\n郭文貴單野爆出來就係到吹奏中資<br />\n怪唔得好多巴打都話01係小罵大幫忙<br />\n連登個吹奏POST第一頁第一個提中資福利好<br />\n之前就吹奏過移民大陸<br />\n今次郭文貴單野都好重視<br />\n用左唔少打手<br />\n<br />\n最後講唔好太短視<br />\n半年我記得就有兩單新聞<br />\n中資最後會真係請香港人?<br />\n就連左派團體之前都話用返大陸人<br />\n香港班土共都俾人當避孕套<br />\n<br />\n中飛內地工程師佔半數 考試易過本地人<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161125/55965218\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161125%2F55965218&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=625c6fb1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161125%2F55965218&h=80a21600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161125/55965218</a><br />\n中飛新編更制度唔覆當應承 李卓人批霸王硬上弓<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161125/55965041\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161125%2F55965041&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=fa89b82d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20161125%2F55965041&h=788277f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20161125/55965041</a><br />\n<br />\n樂香園：中資行賤招逼走港人<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20160606/19642744\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20160606%2F19642744&d=kK8wO%2BHHGyY98lbbYtfopdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=4a41a446\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20160606%2F19642744&h=455771b3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20160606/19642744</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a707257fe292239bb0bb05cacd2d7cd46dc786f5","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:48:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc86cce0f8714d445658acebe22d3b8c7faf17b","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:51:31.000Z","msg":"香港海底撈招聘日僅一人應徵　冀表演「拉麵」<br />\n<br />\n內地知名火鍋連鎖店「海底撈」將在港開設分店，今日（4日）起一連7日舉辦招聘日，聘請近百人，所有職位薪金由12800元起，包括服務員、廚師等。「海底撈」職員要「精通十八般武藝」，包括唱歌、表演拉麵等，而在香港分店的招聘日首天反應一般，整個早上僅1人來應徵，直言「表演拉麵有咩好驚？好好玩！」。「海底撈」董事助理趙先生解釋，「海底撈」服務要求較高，與香港一般食肆不同，故應徵人不多是意料中事。<br />\n<br />\n「海底撈」於今日起至本月10日舉行招聘日。員工薪金以12800元起跳，佣金則由「計件工資」的方法計算，即多勞多得，而卓越員工薪金近可達二萬元。<br />\n<br />\n應徵者愛吃海底撈　冀表演「拉麵」<br />\n現年28歲的張先生今早10時半到現場應徵，成為招聘日唯一的應徵者。他表示，他非常喜愛吃「海底撈」，過去曾光顧10多次，早前聽聞香港打算開設「海底撈」時，更一心決定「要試下」。他指出，自己具有4年的入廚經驗，打算應徵廚師一職。對於廚師要為顧客表演「拉麵」，他直言「表演拉麵有咩好驚？好好玩！可以互動冇咁悶。」<br />\n<br />\n剝蝦殼最簡單　唱歌最難<br />\n海底撈董事助理趙先生表示，「海底撈」服務要求較高，與香港一般食肆的運作模式不同，或因而令香港應徵者卻步，「要替客人剝蝦殼只屬簡單程度，最難則是唱歌。」他續指，「海底撈」職員要猜度顧客的心意，並主動為客人製造驚喜，「如在客人言談中得知他們生日，職員需要送上蛋糕。若客人喜歡吃西瓜，亦需要主動送上。」<br />\n<br />\n海底撈所有職位薪金由$12,800起跳，實際按職位、經驗及能力而定；另外也跟隨內地海底撈慣例設有「計件工資」，即多勞多得，招聘廣告更指表現卓越員工薪金可達20,000元；福利方面，全職員工享每月300元交通津貼、介紹一名新員工可獲100元介紹費、入職滿三年，每年可獲3,000元至6,000元子女教育津貼、部分職員享每月600元以上父母補貼、店經理更可獲房屋補貼12,000元等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可以搵籍口請大陸人啦"},{"pid":"bf487ed70c0608bbd566366fdb41ee807dff6876","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T12:54:48.000Z","msg":"講起搵籍口請支那人<br />\n當年支那建築請人起高鐵<br />\n係報紙登廣告<br />\n全部都注明要5到十年高鐵經驗<br />\n香港人有鬼<br />\n全世界都無邊個國家有人起過十年高鐵<br />\n根本開D無可能條件話請唔到人<br />\n之後請支那人"},{"pid":"85c3d18a90dad736c919b1c80b1916315bb947a4","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:01:49.000Z","msg":"推下啦<br />\n唔好正評就走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"461f5421e238ddf6d4b071587c226aec6b0431ca","tid":229230,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:05:33.000Z","msg":"幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nhk01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ca3d7aac12ddffc930281557c6eb2291c947ee","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:14:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52f05144c318c4aeba5d4b14ce5be070fd19a077","tid":229230,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:16:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"caa6b42cfd2902b9590af16fe701ec6f8c6e471c","tid":229230,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"301f28318764c92d898b6e5ac7f23543b39e6b60","tid":229230,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:27:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ff822187afa049187f30a6883bbb5d4094ebe668","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:27:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb1b578bc9418e2526fe5aca307144594780ec3f","tid":229230,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:31:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1f5fb104a977f426839a253c24adde3475f288","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:37:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ee0ee161f7b4f0024fab4da745dc2914d35183c","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T13:58:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"629d1258ec9019e4fe76b9a2e27b57d6001ece3f","tid":229230,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:01:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"27bcfa988069c39ce02ac295b37f219e1c44f766","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:10:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc24fd8279fc034e011d7c2433c1a14a4ad30c1","tid":229230,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d19a6c75014c15f5e0e5a6ce86b06397efb4d24","tid":229230,"uid":2867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"係估唔到咁多人吹奏中資姐"},{"pid":"7fff0c5fc8db9c68c2630d84559c195f61ca4899","tid":229230,"uid":77416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:18:38.000Z","msg":"香港人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72bd3ca1fc6f574d0ebb0cf7cd319aeae39ff358","tid":229230,"uid":49456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:19:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb1ac9b51db5c37365473477cce282e5c0851c3","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:20:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係估唔到咁多人吹奏中資姐</blockquote><br />\n係打手帶起先<br />\n頭一頁兩個人一唱一和<br />\n之後有人有相反意見就話人憤青"},{"pid":"8b71ff2db742fe96ee7524f0e69ef47081c24aa0","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T14:30:0