/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566e667ac346d23757d2264863b1adeb583f38c7","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:19:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係估唔到咁多人吹奏中資姐</blockquote><br />\n係打手帶起先<br />\n頭一頁兩個人一唱一和<br />\n之後有人有相反意見就話人憤青</blockquote><br />\n個人覺得佢地唔係吹奏中資，係對比起港資中資係好好多</blockquote><br />\n我係留意到第一個吹奏中資條友我之前都懷疑佢係打手<br />\n先覺個post有可疑<br />\n現在打手都係引導言論<br />\n佢地利用大家不滿達成目標<br />\n佢地只要幾個人就夠"},{"pid":"5acb6dc67ecdd5bc4fa6c44bc89790559e64105f","tid":229230,"uid":37030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:31:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d593a9674c38b3c3cae8f6838b9f67fbfbb001ec","tid":229230,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T15:35:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係估唔到咁多人吹奏中資姐</blockquote><br />\n係打手帶起先<br />\n頭一頁兩個人一唱一和<br />\n之後有人有相反意見就話人憤青</blockquote><br />\n個人覺得佢地唔係吹奏中資，係對比起港資中資係好好多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中資開嘅條件係好，但係香港咁多中國留學生你估人地請你香港人定自己人呀拿？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d450fa776f8a0fcbf84e6b60789ba031086d1b92","tid":229230,"uid":23916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T17:16:37.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a37e8e77beb9d2a0fce2cdbf658b7c075d0dbe","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T22:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c46e9101fda6776ba5a614b96e422281fda84e39","tid":229230,"uid":49359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-04T22:54:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a982c94d1066205af81d48c5116a5327c2cfe9